{"tid":1531973,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［公投］9月14中秋活動做咩好。","createTime":"2019-09-02T11:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T10:43:18.000Z","uid":88306,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b1aa7c0edccdd307d7708c0dadb2cf4b07f1c3a8","tid":1531973,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"依家好似無咩活動了，大家都好似死曬氣咁。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於下星期就係中秋佳節。<br />\n我地係咪應該諗下有咩活動一齊聚首一堂。<br />\n開開心心迎接中秋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮- 偏地賞月，玩月餅，食蠟燭。<br />\n<br />\n負皮- 歡迎大家諗下有咩活動。"},{"pid":"92030e081d7edd729c90d6eaadb612fc40300fd0","tid":1531973,"uid":81066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"食催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1793269921bcdf17cca3bb3b13b40105d5c55575","tid":1531973,"uid":59790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"千其唔好煲蠟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc50be35ac5a786f3762fd3b8ee62393af88dfcb","tid":1531973,"uid":88306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"大家推下諗下啦。<br />\n<br />\n無活動就會慢慢無左道氣架啦。"},{"pid":"5cc715f4af120ac9a71f9a8fdf461dc275b52d18","tid":1531973,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"好想睇中秋節連埋d藍絲廢老比狗話非法集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住玩蠟燭話係暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11002cae7fe1bf93c9ccf9c7593d6696fb447c04","tid":1531973,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"預計中秋會係下一次大搜捕<br />\n自己睇路"},{"pid":"64b45377cfcedb9ed5f76952746b7b85b6aaa820","tid":1531973,"uid":56700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"慶祝還慶祝，大家要小心選擇月餅牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd商業食品就食食為妙啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非，好無力，好忟？<br />\n要抗爭，只有十月一前每日堅持做以下既事，係堅持，每日做，逼自己做，保持憤怒，唔好對暴力麻木，係呢到發誓你堅持呢個九月，就一個月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 全民黑衫加口罩（香港蒙面法都未，唔係已經驚定先呀，試諗吓班黑警日日對住黑衫都會癲）<br />\n2. 罷消費（記得逢星期五同日罷買！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！任何元朗鄉黑開嘅鋪頭、福建幫、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、藍紅食店、紅媒都要罷）好難？勇武難唔難？<br />\n3. 低享樂（要發洩，做運動、十點9叫、唔好taobao消費食好野）<br />\n4. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n5. 每日like and share 1個文宣post<br />\n6. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit)，請習慣retweet with comment and hashtag #PoliceBrutality #HongKongProtests. Also, please usually upvote the posts of Reddit<br />\n7. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。<br />\n8. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n9. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n10. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n11. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n12. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"e531d17f59148424f4b320be7ae51fc080e54338","tid":1531973,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2923328bc1cf00df64c3bd287c0d9805ec169d4","tid":1531973,"uid":210778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:15:17.000Z","msg":"台灣中秋好似中意BBQ"},{"pid":"f28dbb9c02d8d6fdade8f1a1dc40127611ad7069","tid":1531973,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢，大家幫手搵文宣推下中秋佳節活動啦"},{"pid":"1ea48bd1a53177861ca37c1767359d44f6810be8","tid":1531973,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧鳴而死 不默而生<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1e294771ab1ffedc88ec1b2903fcf31b28e7f77d","tid":1531973,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:05:18.000Z","msg":"點解成個9月好似再無活動？"},{"pid":"7381c5ecfec6171e72adad6964b082141105e6b1","tid":1531973,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:05:50.000Z","msg":"人人拎一支空白紙燈籠